detail.name: Great Ape Baby
detail.effect:
[On Play] Play up to 1 Battle Card with a cost of 2 or less from your hand.
[When Attacking] Choose up to 1 Battle Card with a cost of 3 or less and place it into its owner's Combo Area.

detail.name: 大猿ベビー
detail.traits: マシンミュータント/サイヤ人/大猿
detail.effect: 【登場時】自分の手札のコスト2以下のバトルカード1枚までを登場させる。【アタック時】バトルエリアのコスト3以下のバトルカード1枚までを選び、持ち主のコンボエリアに置く。

Does the [Auto] skill on your opponent's FB03-121 <Bardock> activate?
